high_descs: wash and remove potato from sink
Move forward to the sink, turn right, go to the microwave on the counter.
Take the potato out of the mike.
Turn around, bring the potato to the sink on the right.
Wash the potato in the sink.
Bring the washed potato to the fridge on the right.
Put the washed potato in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed potato in the fridge.

high_descs: Go forward to the microwave on the right

Turn left and go to the sink
Put the potato in the sink, turn on the water, turn off the water and remove the potato from the sink
Turn right and go to the refrigerator on the left
Put the potato in the refrigerator to the right of the pot
